{"tid":477671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大佬B東山再起建飲食王國","createTime":"2017-11-23T08:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T09:43:33.000Z","uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15cccef0a99be246f1708a5182be2509f2737ec8","tid":477671,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"喺《反黑》飾演淡出江湖、享受家庭生活嘅「大B哥」，係吳志雄依家生活寫照。由縱橫黑道，到淡出轉投影壇，經歷生意失敗，落難再翻生嘅志雄哥，喺內地建立連鎖西餐廳、火鍋店、自家湯包、酒店嘅飲食王國。前塵日子擔驚受怕，下月六張嘅大佬B，食嘅係安樂茶飯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171122/large/1511362599_1a08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171122%2Flarge%2F1511362599_1a08.jpg&h=93d30604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171122/large/1511356312_15d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171122%2Flarge%2F1511356312_15d3.jpg&h=20394e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171122/large/1511356307_6cb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171122%2Flarge%2F1511356307_6cb1.jpg&h=0c178160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171122/large/1511356237_b641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171122%2Flarge%2F1511356237_b641.jpg&h=5f9fa405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171122/large/1511356234_7e09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171122%2Flarge%2F1511356234_7e09.jpg&h=3796ce5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬B曾經食住「古惑仔」系列名利雙收，有過幾千萬身家，但投資失利同爛賭，令佢輸剩一層樓。不過再霉都好，江湖出身義字行頭，兄弟唔可以唔幫！<br />\n「總之人哋嗌我一聲大佬就當人兄弟，以前個義字仲緊要過家庭，我老婆成日因為咁鬧我，『屋企兩斗米都無，你都可以為咗出面，打家劫舍你都可以為咗出面啲兄弟有飯食，屋企米都無，你都唔會為吓屋企。』有咁樣話過我。」<br />\n<br />\n但當自己有難時，大佬B先發現所謂兄弟，只會敷衍話幫你諗吓，最終屋企先係真正嘅避風港。「人情冷暖係應該架，你落難人哋咩事要幫你呢？唔係一定要幫你架，係咪先？」老婆就唔同喇！「攞晒啲首飾、賣晒啲樓俾我還債，同埋話：『我跟得你，有同冇都係一樣。』我咪話佢聽囉：『你放心，你老公咁聰明，得啦你放心，我一定會還番晒俾你。』」<br />\n<br />\n大佬B後生靠拳頭、揸刀搵食，近年再靠一把刀，不過係餐刀，三年前喺深圳開主題西餐廳。「搞主題餐廳啦，一搞就中喇，搞吓搞吓就咁多間出嚟。」<br />\n從此飲食王國愈做愈有，除咗推出自家湯包，本月喺江蘇又開正宗港式火鍋店，下個月又話開多間麵店，仲有同人合資嘅酒店。阿嫂終於守得雲開。<br />\n<br />\n雖然東山再起，但大佬B亦寫咗一首打油詩提醒自己：「貧窮說話牙無力，富貴嬌人鼻有聲；有魚有肉朋友多，有錢需記沒錢時；落難何曾見幾人，人來求我三春雨，我求別人六月霜。」<br />\n難怪佢話朋友之間唔再講錢銀，搞生意都只同親人合作，皆因嘗盡人情冷暖。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20171123/560352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20171123%2F560352&d=vvZaVjXVMljUr7jM103PqHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e7b49f39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20171123%2F560352&h=eb173a5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20171123/560352</a>"},{"pid":"ece9f18c3711f062414484845244a4fc044ee7c6","tid":477671,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"認真，間間都唔同辦數，似係亂咁投資，隨時又一鋪俾人清袋"},{"pid":"1c0b25bd0a9110f939609f0c59aa49f743c80d7c","tid":477671,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"貧窮說話牙無力，富貴嬌人鼻有聲；有魚有肉朋友多，有錢需記沒錢時；落難何曾見幾人，人來求我三春雨，我求別人六月霜<br />\n<br />\n李杜再世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af6b5c286f6ad5cc87ead300db00dab86226018","tid":477671,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T09:38:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb9915377806472a9878afbbb1708978886877de","tid":477671,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/174216_67a07562baaa9cd68bb893b091c08a36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F174216_67a07562baaa9cd68bb893b091c08a36.jpg&h=d60ad2ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5602b593fa6d3978b916e99ab23f8a199ceb2ea9","tid":477671,"uid":99135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/174331_d287dc4db512b6a6d851dcf79a2d17d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F174331_d287dc4db512b6a6d851dcf79a2d17d7.jpg&h=67cae20d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}